    • Method Detail

      • build

        @NonNull
public ACRAConfiguration build()
                                  throws ACRAConfigurationException
        Builds the ACRAConfiguration which will be used to configure ACRA.

        You can pass this ConfigurationBuilder to ACRA.init(Application, ConfigurationBuilder) and ACRA.init(Application, ConfigurationBuilder) will handle any Exception.

        Returns:
        new ACRAConfiguration containing all the properties configured on this builder.
        Throws:
        ACRAConfigurationException - if the required values for the configured notification mode have not been provided.
